    "As an extension, GNN-RAG can be combined with prompt optimization (Wen et al., 2023; Zhang et al., 2023a) so that the LLM understands the graph better.",
    "Moreover, the scope of our GNN-RAG contributions is to improve the retrieval results over the KG without specialized GNN-LLM interactions.",
    "However, the GNN and the LLM could be coupled via iterative retrieval (Asai et al., 2023) to further improve KGQA.",
    "Zhang et al., 2024b), where the Llama-7B-Chat model is trained to generate to generate a list of answers for KGQA.",
    "We follow RoG (Luo et al., 2024a) fine-tuning approach."
